WEBVTT

00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:06.500
THEY ARE FOUR OF THE
MOST COMMON

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.830
PLANTS WE KNOW.

00:00:08.830 --> 00:00:12.460
WE'VE ALWAYS THOUGHT
THAT WE CONTROLLED THEM.

00:00:12.460 --> 00:00:16.530
BUT WHAT IF, IN FACT,
THEY HAVE BEEN SHAPING US?

00:00:16.530 --> 00:00:20.360
Man: WE DON'T GIVE NEARLY
ENOUGH CREDIT TO PLANTS.

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:21.430
THEY'VE BEEN WORKING ON US,

00:00:21.430 --> 00:00:23.760
THEY'VE BEEN USING US,
FOR THEIR OWN PURPOSES.

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:27.630
Narrator: FOUR PLANTS THAT HAVE
TRAVELED THE ROAD TO SUCCESS,

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:31.130
BY SATISFYING HUMAN DESIRES.

00:00:31.130 --> 00:00:32.760
Man: THE TULIP,

00:00:32.760 --> 00:00:36.600
BY GRATIFYING OUR DESIRE FOR
A CERTAIN KIND OF BEAUTY,

00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:37.830
HAS GOTTEN US

00:00:37.830 --> 00:00:41.100
TO TAKE IT FROM ITS
ORIGINS IN CENTRAL ASIA

00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:44.360
AND DISPERSE IT
AROUND THE WORLD.

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:49.130
MARIJUANA, BY GRATIFYING OUR
DESIRE TO CHANGE CONSCIOUSNESS,

00:00:49.130 --> 00:00:51.760
HAS GOTTEN PEOPLE
TO RISK THEIR LIVES,

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:53.300
THEIR FREEDOM, IN ORDER TO

00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:55.700
GROW MORE OF IT AND
PLANT MORE OF IT.

00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:59.430
THE POTATO -- BY GRATIFYING
OUR DESIRE FOR CONTROL,

00:00:59.430 --> 00:01:02.160
CONTROL OVER NATURE, SO
THAT WE CAN FEED OURSELVES,

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:06.960
HAS GOTTEN ITSELF
OUT OF SOUTH AMERICA

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:08.330
AND EXPANDED ITS RANGE

00:01:08.330 --> 00:01:11.960
FAR BEYOND WHERE IT
WAS 500 YEARS AGO.

00:01:11.960 --> 00:01:13.530
AND THE APPLE,

00:01:13.530 --> 00:01:15.760
BY GRATIFYING OUR
DESIRE FOR SWEETNESS --

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:18.700
BEGINS IN THE
FORESTS OF KAZAKHSTAN

00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:22.130
AND IS NOW THE UNIVERSAL FRUIT.

00:01:22.130 --> 00:01:23.800
THESE ARE GREAT WINNERS

00:01:23.800 --> 00:01:26.060
IN THE DANCE OF DOMESTICATION.

00:01:26.060 --> 00:01:30.060
NarTHE WAY YOU'VE
NEVERURE SEEN IT BEFORE,

00:01:30.060 --> 00:01:38.130
WITH BEST-SELLING
AUTHOR MICHAEL POLLAN.

