Man: AND THIS RELATIONSHIP
OF THE PLANTS,

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:42.960
LEARNING HOW TO
GRATIFY OUR DESIRES,

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:45.830
AND OUR WORKING FOR THEM
IN EXCHANGE FOR THIS,

00:01:45.830 --> 00:01:54.200
IS WHAT I CALL THE
BOTANY OF DESIRE.

