AND WE DON'T WANT TO PUT
ANYTHING ON THE FOOD

01:39:26.530 --> 01:39:31.430
THAT WE EAT ANY MORE
-- TO TAINT IT FOR US,
ANY MORE THAN YOU.

01:39:31.430 --> 01:39:36.930
Pollan: YOU KNOW, THE CONTROL
OF NATURE IS EXPENSIVE.

01:39:36.930 --> 01:39:40.200
TO SPRAY ALL THOSE PESTICIDES,
TO HAVE 10 SPRAYINGS

01:39:40.200 --> 01:39:42.630
OF FERTILIZER OVER A
